Subject: Re: Shashank Shekhar - ShareChat EF Mining

=20

Adding views from the meeting below:

=20

TD

- good guy but don=E2=80=99t see an EF

- strong content experience and good operator=20

- he has said 6-12 months so maybe track and once we know idea can evaluate=
 deeper

- thoughtful and curios=20

- explorer archetype - political consulting, solar startup, Sharechat conte=
nt Ops

=20

RC

+ Ticks the hygiene boxes =E2=80=93 pedigree + experience within a large tech + g=
ood track record

+ Has the right intrinsics - comes from a tier 3 town, risk taker

+ Entrepreneurial - started with solar business straight out of IIT + raise=
d capital=20

+ Fast learner  - has had diverse experience - ops heavy (real estate) and =
thin stack businesses (Circle)

+ Basis refs, he=E2=80=99s got a good Followership - he is well respected=20

? Unclear if he is a large business builder=20

? Unique Insights were missing from his journey =E2=80=93 learnings from Circle w=
ere obvious + does not seem to know much about Public (their shift to video)

=20

Regards,

Rahul

=20

