From: Rahul Chugh <rahul.chugh@matrixpartners.in>
Date: Friday, 29 July 2022 at 2:04 PM
To: Tarun Davda <tarun@matrixpartners.in>
Cc: Ayush Chamaria <ayush@matrixpartners.in>
Subject: Shashank Shekhar - ShareChat EF Mining

=20

TD,

=20

Starting the thread on Shashank Shekhar =E2=80=93 potential EF from SC. Sharing v=
iews and refs below:

=20

Likelihood of starting-up =E2=80=93 Medium=20

Timeline =E2=80=93 6-12 months

Next steps =E2=80=93
Set up for TD after a few more informal refs from SC=20
=20

Refs
Ref from current SC folks:
Good followership within SC=20
Sagar (ex-Head of Growth at SC, joined Cashfree last month) would want to j=
oin him if and when he starts up
Most likely to start up among senior SC folks=20
Ops and business spike =E2=80=93 above average
Doing very well at SC=20
Entrepreneurial mindset
Past refs from SC folks (done during Circle News eval)
Strengths
Above average IQ, analytical, logical reasoning=20
Creative =E2=80=93 good at content himself (writes poems, etc.)
Challenges
Intuition-driven =E2=80=93 lasted long with SC pre-Circle because of friendship w=
ith Farid (batchmates from IITK)
EQ =E2=80=93 Big ego and aloof from colleagues=20
Rumoured to have been asked to leave SC (pre- Circle News)
=20

MPI Views

TD (Aug=E2=80=9918)

+ good fit for top of the stack kind of businesses (seems to have meandered=
 at other stuff like grabhouse, agri equipment rental etc)

+ strong experience at one of the best media / content companies (sharechat=
) and had a good POV on content diversity, seeding user behaviour, PGC v/s U=
GC etc

+ Good structured answer on differentiation vs Dailyhunt

+ Sensed a quiet intensity

+ Farid BRC

? Too verbose at times =E2=80=93 clarity of thought issue?

? Unclear spike?

=20

Relative to Subodh not clear to me who is the guy to back =E2=80=93 feel both hav=
e their strengths and we need to spend more IDS time with both to develop a =
strong POV

=20

Avi (Aug=E2=80=9918)

+ Like him more than Lokal guys

? Scrappier

+ Sharechat exp is relevant

? Still like Subodh more=20

=20

RC (May=E2=80=9922)

+ Pedigreed

+ Potential EF =E2=80=93 unclear how much money he=E2=80=99s made from sale of Circle t=
o SC

+ Ops and content spike basis current refs

+ Good insights on new content initiatives =E2=80=93 livestreaming, etc.

? Past SC refs =E2=80=93 rumoured to have been asked to leave; big ego and social=
ly aloof from colleagues=20

=20

Regards,

Rahul

=20


